Running Instructions:

Running the server:
1) cd Ex2/server
2) npm install
3) node server.js

Running the client:
1) cd Ex2
2) In order to change the screen id (The default value is 3), open 'js/main.js' file and change line 6 to the wanted value (var screenId = 3;)
3) Open Google Chrome (WinKey + R and run the command: 'chrome.exe --user-data-dir="C:/Chrome dev session" --disable-web-security')
4) In Google Chrome, run the 'index.html' file: 'http://localhost:8080/index.html'

